<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Sulakshna Home Products</title>

<style>
body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: #fffaf0;
}

header {
    background-color: #b22222;
    color: white;
    padding: 15px;
    text-align: center;
}

nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    background: #ffcc00;
    padding: 10px;
}

nav a {
    margin: 0 15px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: black;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 50px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffefba, #ffffff);
}

.hero h1 {
    font-size: 40px;
    color: #b22222;
}

.products {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 20px;
}

.card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 15px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.card img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 10px;
}

.about, .contact {
    padding: 30px;
    text-align: center;
}

footer {
    background: #b22222;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 10px;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Sulakshna Home Products</h1>
    <p>Pure, Homemade, Jain-Friendly Goodness</p>
</header>

<nav>
    <a href="#">Home</a>
    <a href="#products">Products</a>
    <a href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
    <h1>Authentic Homemade Products</h1>
    <p>No Onion • No Garlic • Jain Friendly</p>
</section>

<section id="products" class="products">

    <div class="card">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200" alt="Chilli Powder">
        <h3>Chilli Powder</h3>
        <p>Fresh, spicy, and pure.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200" alt="Haldi Powder">
        <h3>Haldi Powder</h3>
        <p>Rich color and natural purity.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200" alt="Masala Powder">
        <h3>Masala Powder</h3>
        <p>Traditional homemade blend.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200" alt="Papad">
        <h3>Papad</h3>
        <p>Crispy and delicious.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200" alt="Shevayya">
        <h3>Shevayya</h3>
        <p>Perfect for sweet dishes.</p>
    </div>

</section>

<section id="about" class="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>
        Sulakshna Home Products brings you homemade, hygienic and Jain-friendly food products.
        We ensure no onion, no garlic, and no root vegetables are used.
    </p>
</section>

<section id="contact" class="contact">
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>📞 Phone: 9876543210</p>
    <p>💬 WhatsApp: 9876543210</p>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 Sulakshna Home Products</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
